thread.title_full: Javier Baez Gets A Big Tattoo To Commemorate Cubs’ Historic Championship

author: Sports – CBS Chicago
title: Javier Baez Gets A Big Tattoo To Commemorate Cubs’ Historic Championship
text:
Javier Baez Gets A Big Tattoo To Commemorate Cubs’ Historic Championship February 24, 2017 1:14 PM Cubs infielder Javier Baez. (Getty Images) 
(CBS) Cubs infielder Javier Baez has commemorated the team’s historic World Series title in 2016 in style. 
With a big tattoo on the upper part of his left arm. #Cubs Baez has new tattoo, just finished it last night pic.twitter.com/mwxGJfT2Fi
